---
// About component - Two-column layout with asymmetric image grid
---

<section class="about-section py-20 md:py-32">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <!-- Main Grid -->
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
      <!-- Left Column - Text Content -->
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
        <h2 class="fade-up mb-6 font-serif text-5xl font-bold leading-tight md:text-6xl">
          About Us
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-charcoal/80">
          <p class="fade-up">
            We are a collective of architects and designers dedicated to creating spaces that inspire and endure.
            Our approach blends contemporary innovation with timeless principles, resulting in environments that
            feel both fresh and familiar.
          </p>
          <p class="fade-up">
            Every project begins with understanding the unique story of place and purpose. We believe great
            architecture emerges from the dialogue between vision and context, ambition and restraint.
          </p>
          <p class="fade-up">
            Our work spans residential, commercial, and cultural projects, each one a testament to our commitment
            to craft, sustainability, and the human experience of space.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column - Asymmetric Image Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:gap-6">
        <!-- Large Image -->
        <div class="fade-up col-span-2 overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src="https://picsum.photos/800/600?architecture"
            alt="Architecture 1"
            class="parallax-img h-full w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Two Small Images -->
        <div class="fade-up overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src="https://picsum.photos/400/500?building"
            alt="Architecture 2"
            class="parallax-img h-full w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="fade-up overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src="https://picsum.photos/400/500?interior"
            alt="Architecture 3"
            class="parallax-img h-full w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Medium Image -->
        <div class="fade-up col-span-2 overflow-hidden md:col-span-1">
          <img
            src="https://picsum.photos/500/400?design"
            alt="Architecture 4"
            class="parallax-img h-full w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
